song.title: Angels Come, You're Dead
song.info:
In few days, i finished lot of Dream music titles, here is the third in 4 days and for that time, great and intersting songs. The ideas here was… You’re dead. And the angles come to drop you to the paradise. Still mixing piano’s melodies and techno rave sounds… but here with the help of a flute pan and some Drum n bass rhythm.
